{"tid":807853,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"周嘉儀黃紫盈轉投亞視","createTime":"2018-09-06T01:03:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T09:49:47.000Z","uid":130105,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"78c4e9a4c4778b92005019f3f7708a260f2f3b77","tid":807853,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T01:03:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1BRoQ29m5ZiUVO7cQZVtpJnHLq11qxO_N\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1BRoQ29m5ZiUVO7cQZVtpJnHLq11qxO_N&h=0d726960&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://video.cdn.on.cc/video/201809/OEN180905-8524-1908-M_ipad.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvideo.cdn.on.cc%2Fvideo%2F201809%2FOEN180905-8524-1908-M_ipad.mp4&d=mE4S28PVtkN9fbRuvdd6pSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=f2bff67f\" target=\"_blank\">http://video.cdn.on.cc/video/201809/OEN180905-8524-1908-M_ipad.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1B0-FdNhKt5SMKEUlllP1lv5yEaDX6MW0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1B0-FdNhKt5SMKEUlllP1lv5yEaDX6MW0&h=ec52079e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1n7llbExoLSJv7x8ZesimI5ZRoebrdGjR\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1n7llbExoLSJv7x8ZesimI5ZRoebrdGjR&h=1452dfcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1PATbOkGddNDTyfW4jJv8pQCM3e1iP3eu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1PATbOkGddNDTyfW4jJv8pQCM3e1iP3eu&h=9d9f6859&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1YLHwyu3jFyIDIzxgFJcDbtuBnlsaf9fo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1YLHwyu3jFyIDIzxgFJcDbtuBnlsaf9fo&h=79bb186e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1AeeFIyPssTh2b2dEoPNMYXqXEnD_BTn2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1AeeFIyPssTh2b2dEoPNMYXqXEnD_BTn2&h=392f23ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n周嘉儀（左）同黃紫盈齊齊倒戈！<br />\n<br />\n前無綫兩大女神主播周嘉儀和黃紫盈今日齊現身亞視，宣布她們擔任新節目《香港追擊搜》主持。當嘉儀表示大家是同期主播時，黃紫盈笑着反問：「同期？」嘉儀才補充：「我早佢幾年。」黃紫盈即刻叫了聲「師姐」。<br />\n<br />\n兩人先後離開無綫後，亦曾有合作做主持，不過是次新節目則會較少碰頭機會。對於入亞視，嘉儀說：「今日早咗入嚟化妝，同佢講開，原來佢又係喺化妝間，但大家隔住一面牆見唔到。（覺得同以前無綫分別好大？）拍攝都係咁進行，同事都好專業，好有交帶，分別不大。」<br />\n<br />\n而黃紫盈同樣表示沒有大分別，指是網絡媒體，合作好快上手，問到酬勞如何？她說：「唔錯，有誠意，好開心。（價錢開心過以前？）開心」嘉儀亦表示非主要向錢看，自言好耐沒有在幕前出現，希望獲得滿足感，兩人均表示希望做個好節目，緊要過錢。<br />\n<br />\n來源 source: <a href=\"http://hk.on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc&d=mE4S28PVtkN9fbRuvdd6pSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=cb42988d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc</a><br />\n<br />\n+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++<br />\n<br />\n亞視唔係執緊咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"461aeb9f90acbf96088d5b692cf9452318881921","tid":807853,"uid":20816,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T01:28:17.000Z","msg":"嘉儀老咗又肥咗，不了"},{"pid":"68b181e8b545e522646f6cdaa3c8f70bec0b8d85","tid":807853,"uid":48631,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T01:35:43.000Z","msg":"兩隻G"},{"pid":"b111558b51833386effdc6fe34b26b6d4c4b1286","tid":807853,"uid":42820,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T01:36:49.000Z","msg":"老女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2e3953a491132c326cee1243370ee06e004c41c","tid":807853,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T01:38:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n..,亞視唔係執緊咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n復活咗啦"},{"pid":"707358d3482e6bbf7d962aea443d556ce3813550","tid":807853,"uid":20286,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09